&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint motivated and enthusiastic Band 6 Nurses ideally with leadership experience though not essential as full support and training will be provided for senior band 5 nurses who are able to demonstrate the necessary knowledge and skills to fulfil this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have 2 neonatal units, level 2 at Barnet Hospital site with 30 cots including Intensive care and High dependency cots. A level 1 Neonatal unit at The Royal Free Hospital site with 14 Special Care cots. The units have friendly, motivated and dynamic teams that promote developmental care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We currently have vacancies on the Barnet site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We would be delighted to show you around the unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
